Problem Statement :A new fitness startup wants to launch an app for
busy office professionals who struggle to find
time for exercise. Before designing a single pixel, the team needs to understand the "User’s Pain.
Act as a UX Researcher and define the
target audience.
Create User Personas (Age, goals, frustrations).
Build an Empathy Map (What do they see,

think, feel, and do?).

